thread.title: Michael Hartog

author: Michael Hartog
title: Michael Hartog
text:
My business partner & I decided to take an entry level package at Servcorp Wollongong last July 2016. We'd meet up a couple of times a week and use their brand new state-of-the-art facilities.
As our business grown, we now have an office suite & use utilise Servcorp staff (Alex Cassidy - who is an asset to us & Servcorp).
We could not be happier with our business arrangement at Servcorp Wollongong & highly recommend to any business wanting to look at relocating in Wollongong area.
